WEBVTT

00:01:29.163 --> 00:01:30.996
The doorbell rang,

00:01:31.996 --> 00:01:34.663
a ring that could have saved a life.

00:01:36.413 --> 00:01:39.829
"Beat." is our project exploring
the ominous silence

00:01:39.829 --> 00:01:42.079
surrounding domestic violence.

00:01:42.121 --> 00:01:45.704
We filmed the experiment,
and it became instantly viral.

00:01:45.746 --> 00:01:48.038
Our campaign amplified
the voices of survivors

00:01:48.038 --> 00:01:50.079
who shared similar stories online.

00:01:50.663 --> 00:01:52.788
It equipped neighbors
with specific advice,

00:01:52.829 --> 00:01:54.829
and many committed to taking action.

00:01:55.621 --> 00:01:58.371
In a country where every other week,

00:01:58.371 --> 00:02:01.371
the ground quietly embraces
the body of a woman